      "content": "it's just not the same though. people say things to be nice, but in reality, they'll just pity me. they'll look at me and see a ghost. honestly, staying at the bottom feels more peaceful than trying to pretend everything is okay when it clearly isn't. there's a certain kind of quiet in just giving up.",
